Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody makes some mistakes,{人間のあやまちは誰にもあるが}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you break a precious plate of all things, you just have to die!{事もあろうに落として割れたる過方のお皿お前は手打ちじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Count got madly furious{怒りに怒った老伯爵}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point Benio couldn't help but take all remaining plates and tear them apart!{ならば残り九人分の命を引き受けようと過方のお皿はこのみじん}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this just added fuel to the fire and the stubborn Count stated that Benio had to die as well!{頑固一徹老伯爵は油に火を注がれてべにおも死ねよと待ったなし}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio can only rely on Shinobu, who is, however, staying still and dumbfounded.{唯一頼りのshoui殿腰が抜けたか起したか ただ呆然と立ちんぼう}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio can't back out anymore and she blames Shinobu for that.{後に引けないハイからサンは恨みますぞえshoui殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.76,Sign,,0,0,167,,{\c&HE1DCDF&\bord0\blur1\b1\fs53.333}Farewell, failed bride{いざさらば落第花嫁}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, en garde!{えい覚悟せい}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!{おくさま}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{なんじゃと}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, please wait a minute.{おじいさまちょっとお待ちを}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she trying to sneak off?{このものに及んで逃げを打つのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, Tenmaru, Chimaru.{心配はいらないよ天丸ちまる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio must have a plan on her mind.{べにおさんには何か考えがあってのことだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?{なんと}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Benio!{べ べにおさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Count.{お待たせいたしましたおじいさま}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can continue.{さどうぞお切りくださいんん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready.{良い覚悟じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, begone!{では参るぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Benio is going to die!{べ べにおさんが斬られちゃう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept your fate!{観念せい}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for what awaits you.{お父様,ばばあや,先立つ不幸を許しください}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma'am, we need to stop them right now!{おおくさま早くお止めしなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No.{いいえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Are you letting Benio die?{えではべにおさまを斬らせるのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd really do it?{切れるものですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is waiting for someone to stop him.{ご前は誰か止める人を待っているのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in stopping me, so nobody dare stop me!{止めても無駄だ誰も止めるでないぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's getting too awkward now,{よしもうだいぶ薬が効いたようだ - idk what he meant by this, I'll go with the italian version which should be correct}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go help.{この辺で助け舟を出そう}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Tenmaru, Chimaru!{行け天丸ちまる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, now these dogs, to make it worse!{ええ\Nえこの犬の分際で邪魔立てすると}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll split you open too!{己らも叩き切るぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, he is relieved by this intrusion!{本当は邪魔立てしてもらってほっとしてるのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, it's enough.{おじいさまもういいでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu? This is not your time to be here.{しのぶかお前の出る幕ではない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be so stubborn.{そんな強情を張らずに}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like this is settled.{どうやら一本決まったようですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?{何}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This ends with...{この勝負おじいさまの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,your loss.{負けですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious plates of a lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you've already done a lot.{べにおさんももう十分でしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Don't just shut up and watch! Why couldn't you do something earlier?{あなたねえ見てたんなら黙ってないで\Nもっと早く止めてくれたらどうなんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so frightened, you know!?{私だって本当はおっかなかったんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite that, you didn't lift a finger!{それなのにあんたったら立って見てただけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since nobody cares about me, I'll just go home!{あの私をおきりにならないのなら\N私家に帰ります}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?{本当}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong to this house anymore.{もうこんな家ごめんですあなただって}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go away, you'll be able to marry with the one you really like, right?{私が出ていけば好きな人と結婚できるでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right, please listen to me.{それは違うんだ聞いてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop her, Shinobu!{止めるな忍}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Shinobu!{さようならshoui}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Benio!{待ってべにおさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's get going, Ushigorou!{さあ行きましょうushigorou}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!{がってんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There, go ahead.{さあどうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, wait just a minute!{べにおさん待ってください}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me, it'd be pointless!{止めないで止めたってだめですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I won't.{ええ止めませんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this, Benio.{忘れ物ですよべにおさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my mourning dress.{あ、白い喪服}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{そうですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, you'll be part of the Ijuuin family.{\i0}{これからはお前も伊集院家の人間}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In case something happens to him, you'll have to wear this.{\i0}{shinobu-kunにまいちのことがあった時この白いも服を使いなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Benio... \N- Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother- no, Countess Ijuuin,{おばあさま、いえijuuin伯爵夫人様 - calling sb else's grandmother "grandmother" sounds weird in english but I couldn't think of other ways}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm resentful towards you.{私を恨み申し上げます}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you,{だっておばあさまと、いえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Countess Ijuuin, once were in love with my grandfather{移住院伯爵夫人と私のお爺様が昔恋をなさって}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and since you hoped that it would flourish someday,{その恋をいつか実らせようなんてお考えになったから}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I, a totally naive girl, have to go through this.{私は、私はこんな目にあうのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it,{何も知らない私は}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to think about possible tragedies{父からひとたびとついたら岐阜にまみえるべからずと}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and my Father made me bring this mourning dress.{こんな喪服を持たされてきました}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I... I...{そして、そして}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,had to go through painful times.{悲しい思いもしなければならないのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{どっか自分の恋を孫の代で実らせようなんて気まぐれは二度と}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't make this happen ever again.{二度と起こさないでくださいませ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about{何も知らない一人の娘}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how much this could hurt a naive girl like me?{どんなに傷つけるか\Nお考えになったことがあるのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Countess Ijuuin.{移住院伯爵夫人}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, please stop calling me Countess Ijuuin,{べにおさんその移住院伯爵夫人というのだけはやめてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,please call me {おばあさまと呼んで}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything.{何も言いません}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Countess!{さようなら、伯爵夫人}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, then, let's go.{待たせたわね\Nさあ、行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the only ones who are sad about me leaving this house.{この家で私との別れを悲しんでくれるのはお前たちだけね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In this house animals are better than people, eh?{この家じゃ人間よりも動物の方がよっぽどまともなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{そういうこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't follow me.{だめ、ついてきちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come. This is an order, got it?{来ちゃいけないのよ\Nこれは命令よ わかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go! Go-go-go-go-go!{あらやっと あららららえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Tenmaru, Chimaru!{さようなら、天丸、千丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, aren't you going to stop me?{Shoui、引き止めてくれないんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand, Tenmaru, Chimaru.{分かってくれ、天丸、千丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that time will solve everything.{いずれ必ず時間が解決してくれる}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyono! Hyono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hyono District{氷嚢屋 - is this a bridge/town name? idk, but 屋 is usually some shop/cafe}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, today's such a lovely day!{親分今日はなんてめでてえ日だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta have a toast!{祝杯をあげなくちゃね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinobu...{何さ、何さ、Shouiなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you, don't make Benio drink any alcohol!{だめよ、弁優さんにお酒なんか飲ませちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what'd happen!{知らんなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's such a nice day!{だっておめえ、こんなめでてえ日によ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's have some anmitsu.{じゃあ、あんみつで乾杯しましょうよ // or something like "fruit salad" if you prefer}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anmitsu!?{あんみつ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, how girly can you be?{ranmaru、おめえどこまで女っぽくできてんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you don't understand.{あら、認識不足ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,While my body is a boy's, my mind is a traditional woman's.{私、体は男でも心は劣気としたやまとなでしこなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a body and a mind too, you know?{私は身も心もんなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she is again!{出ました}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,Famous bean soup \NRenowned onigiri {おしるこ秀 おにぎり川 - shiruko; sweet red-bean soup with mochi​, don't really know what 川 stands for here, not 100% sure about 秀 either}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,Famous Renowned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I eat this, I'm not a fan...{所(?)なんていくら食ったって気分でねえや}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, something wrong with your stomach?{親分、腹の具合でもおかしいんじゃないすか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.{いいえ、別に}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! As I thought, we gotta drink!{分かった!やっぱりこれでなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's spice it up, shall we, Boss?{気分がでねえんでやんしょ\Nね、親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, don't make her think strange things!{ushiさん、寝てる子を起こすようなこと言わないでよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's true that in these tough times{でもやっぱりこんなときにあんみつってのは}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood for anmitsu.{気分が盛り上がらないわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?{でしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!{やめてったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, they make delicious anmitsu here!{お姉さん、ここであんみつおいしいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, hurry up!{お姉さん、はやく}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...{あら}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this is bad!{やべえ、やべえぜこれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ushi...{あ、Ushiさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is of good omen.{あら、縁起がいい茶柱が立ってるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear Lord, please listen to me.{なまんだぶなまんだぶ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, what good things are going to happen today?{奥様、今日は何かいいことがあるかもしれませんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Miss Kichiji.{おめでとう、花の屋きちじさん え?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why congratulations?{何がめでたいんです?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally your time to shine. Shinobu will surely be yours.{いよいよあなたの出番ですイジュン少尉は確かにあなたにお渡ししますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, excuse me.{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!{あ、お嬢さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, I leave the bill to you!{ushiさん、お勘定頼むわねあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is happening?{もし、一体どうしたって言うんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? The betrothal just backfired.{なあに、縁談があだになっただけのことですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say...!?{何ですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put the bill here.{姉さん、お勘定ここに置くぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!{ありがとうございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll borrow your phone.{お姉さん、電話かりますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.{どうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{すみません}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1904, the number of telephone subscribers exceeded 180,000{明治39年、加入台数18万を超えた電話は}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and the number of telephones continued to increase.{その後増加の一頭をたどり}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, am I speaking to the Ijuuin home?{もしもし、IJUUIN伯爵家をお願いします}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1925, after the Great Kanto Earthquake, sales exceeded 870,000 units.{関東大震災後の大正14年には87万台を突破した}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I am Ijuuin...{もしもし、移住院ですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.{ああ、なんだ、君か}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, did you really break your engagement with Benio?{Shouiさん、benioさんと縁組が壊れたって本当ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?{え、どうしてそれを}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to stumble across Benio,{あったんです、benioさんと偶然}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are you okay with letting go of her?{いいんですか、あのお嬢さんを手放して}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio misunderstood something about you.{benioさんは君のことを誤解してるんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, all the more so!{ならなおさらです}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio burst crying{benioさんは心の中で泣いています}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and she said that you could be mine.{Benioさんはshouiを私に譲るようなことを言ってましたけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble and a worthless geisha like me togeher,{家族様としがない芸者風情}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that it could never happen.{ご縁がないことは私が誰よりもよく心得ておりますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the situation,{どんな事情があったにせよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not fair to make such a good girl cry.{あんなきっぷのいいお嬢さんを泣かせていいもんですかね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain now,{今は弁解しないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,however, you'll definitely understand.{ただし、そのうちにきっと分かってもらえる時が来る}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!{あっ、ちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You did {\i1}what?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I broke the engagement, rejoice!{そう、あだになったの、喜んで}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that there'd be good omen...{茶柱が立ったのに、茶柱が}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring me some tea!{おい茶をくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I told you to bring me some tea!{こら、お茶だと言っておるのだ、わしは}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you and those long faces?{な、なんだその方たち そのような顔はしくさって\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to complain!{文句があるなら言うがよい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious to kick out a girl like that?{あんな小娘追い出されて当然じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's never met my father!{所詮、benioは我が家の家父には会わなかったのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And she destroyed all of my precious plates!{わしの皿をこなごなにしおってがらに}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You three! If you have anything to say, tell me!{これ、言いたい言葉あればもうせと言うに}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi, you surely feel me, right?.{え、きさらぎ、その方ならば分かってくれよな}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That unreasonable girl drove you mad all the time, didn't she?{な、あの理不尽な小娘にはその方が一番手を焼いておったようじゃからの\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are correct.{はい、その通りでございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? You are free to say everything you think about her.{そうであろうとも遠慮なく胸にたたんでおったことを吐き出すがよいぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've been working in this mansion for many years,{はい、わたくし長年このお屋敷にお使いして参りましたが}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had never met anyone like her.{あのような方は初めてでございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!{んん、よくぞ申した}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did she do?{で、どうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only one who didn't give in to your obstinacy!{殿様の頑固にお負けにならなかったのもあの方が初めてでございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through some difficulties myself,{わたくしもずいぶんと苦労いたしましたが}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'll never meet anyone quite like her.{あのようなお方はもう二度といらっしゃいますまい}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.{そうですね、本当に}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Benio came here, I thought that things would change...{べにおさんがあらっしゃって何もかもが変わっていくような気がしておりましたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always taken care of Young Master{わたくしは若様のむつきのころより お世話をさせていただきましたが}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wondered whether he'd have a son with Benio,{べにお様が先々若様のお子をお産み遊ばすなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I could continue my job,{それまでずっとお使いしてゆくゆくは}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,raise the child and sing him lullabies...{そのお子にもわたくしが子守唄を歌って差し上げられるなどと}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about this so happily.{心楽しく思ったりしたこともございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's son would be our great-grandchild!{べにおさんのお子はわたくしたちのひまごでございますね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Great-grandchild, eh?{ひまごかや}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you'll never be able to meet him!{でもその子の顔は決してみることがかないません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is also Count's fault!{はい、それもお殿様のせいでございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! It's not like I killed her or anything!{だまれまるでわしが赤ん坊をころしたような言い方はよせい}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you waiting for?{えい、何をぐずぐずしておるのや}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Benio your fiancée?{べ、べにおはお前の許婚ではないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go get her!{早くつれものしてこい}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lord!{お、お殿様}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...{それでは}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say this,{そうおっしゃると思っていました}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but since you usually don't get influenced by others' opinions,{お爺様は他人の意見にはけして動かされるお方ではありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't interfere.{だから水が低きえ流れるように}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you to say those words.{いまのお言葉が出てくるのを待っていたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I dispatch.{行ってまいります}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you changed, Dear, didn't you?{ご前もおかわりになりましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio made you reflect.{べにおさんがかえてくれたのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Meiji Era was a long time ago.{明治は遠くなったのじゃい}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Refill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, it's already the fifth one!{いいかげんになさいませ\Nもう五杯目でございますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother, Nanny?{いいじゃないのよ、ばあや}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I couldn't eat this delicious grilled chicken there!{つくねの焼き鳥なんて向こうじゃ食べられなかったんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to put on airs, for God's sake!{いばってる場合じゃございませんでしょ、まったく}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your father going to say about this?{旦那様がお聞きになったらなんとおっしゃるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting kicked out before marrying...{お嫁に入る前に追い出されたなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so bad for your mother...{ばあやは奥様に申し訳なくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I can't say that I didn't expect this.{ま、こんなことになるんじゃないかとうすうすは思っておりましたがね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? After all that effort to go back home,{なによ、せっかく帰ってきてやったのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at least show some nostalgia.{少しは懐かしそうな顔でもしてみろって}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something you want to talk me about.{しばらくいないうちに言いたいこと言うようになっちゃって - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't meet anymore...{もう会えない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I happen to be in love with Young Master.{Kichijiはね、若様に惚れておりましたのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, I don't care about that womaniser anymore!{もうどうでもいいわ、あんな女たらし}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Shinobu!?{もしかしたらshouiが迎えに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am home.{はい、どうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bummer, it's just dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Benio has?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.{はいそうなんでございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Welcome home, father!{あらお帰りなさい、お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not long since I last saw you, but you got fatter!{あら、しばらく見ないうちにお太りになったみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?{そうかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I slimmed down!{やせたわい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, follow me.{/come over here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you got kicked out?{お前、追い出されたというのは本当か}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, it's a misunderstanding, father.{それは違います、誤解です、お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What, so it wasn't because you got kicked out?{なに、追い出されたのではなかったのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Glad, so glad to hear.{そうかよかったよかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can relax, I wasn't kicked out, I left on my own.{え、喜んでよ\Nおんだされたんじゃなくて、自分からおんでたんですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the same thing, you dumbass!{これなら同じことだなこのバカ者！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, you don't know the whole story!{だ、だって、お父様はご存じないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a haunted house, after all!{まるで、化物屋敷みたいな家なんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? A Count lives there, it can't be so bad!{なにを言うか\N伯爵家ともあろう者がバケモノ屋敷のはずはない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such silly things!{たわけたことを申すな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Hanamura, there was a crazy geezer there.{いいえ、おじさま、すごいじいさまがいるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you that famous girly guy?{お、お前は有名なお引きずりさんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Ranmaru?{蘭丸くんか君は}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been a while, Mr. Hanamura.{はい、お久しぶりでございます、おじさま}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that disgraceful effete look on a boy?{やまとおのこがなんたるハレンチな格好を}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that I'm beautiful?{あら、うるわしいとおっしゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey, back off, you're annoying!{あ、よ、よ、よ、よるよるな、気持ちの悪い}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have nightmares tonight.{今晩うなされそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I had to do it to be close to Benio.{だって、こうでもしなければbenioさんのそばにいられないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Close?{そばに?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we even slept in the same room.{ええ、寝るのも一緒の部屋でした}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so glad...{うれしかったな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?{な、なんと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!!! What is this indecent behaviour!?{Benio、お前はなんと恥ずかしな真似を}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You misunderstood, Father!{ご、誤解です、お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I misunderstand?{何が誤解だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Misunderstandings, misunderstandings...{誤解、誤解とは}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, I stacked these!{できた、五回だって - a wordplay I don't know how to convey better)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddja say!?{なんだと}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you don't understand...{お父様って、わかってないだろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've understood enough.{わかっておるとも}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why I have this dagger here?{この懐剣を何のために持たせたかわかるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After finally parting ways with the stubborn count,{固じじいの老伯爵とたもとをわかってきてみれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio still can't breathe a sigh of relief.{これじゃ全くたまらないでるは涙かため息か}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be one more stubborn man in her own house!{意外や我が家にもう一人頑固おやじがござそうろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,While Benio left the Ijuuin mansion to go back home,{ijuuin家を後にして自分の家に帰ったものの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,her stubborn father can't accept it.{昔形の頑固おやじが許さない}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With no choice left, she runs away to wander about unknown places,{仕方なくなくはいからさんはさんがいに行くあてもないさすらいのたび}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,however, even alcohol can't relieve her from her stress,{だがつもりつもった鬱憤をはらさんものと飲んだ酒が悪かった - idk about this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our youthful and naive High Collar Lady.{知らんも花の乱れ咲き}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time in Here Comes the High Collar Lady:\NPetals of a wandering flower{さすらいの花びら}\N{次回はいからさんが通るさすらいの花びらお楽しみに}
